// 역할 기반 관계 테스트

// 1. 기본 공격 관계 정의
Attack IS RELATION
Attack HAS Attacker (Node)
Attack HAS Victim (Node)
Attack DO
    Victim HAS HP (Victim.HP - Attacker.Damage)
END

// 엔티티 정의
Player IS Entity
Player HAS Damage 25
Player HAS Name "Hero"

Enemy IS Entity
Enemy HAS HP 100
Enemy HAS Name "Goblin"

// 초기 상태
DEBUG GRAPH

// 공격 실행
Player Attack Enemy

